entry.title: Fighting in Russian Border Region Following Incursion Enters Second Day
entry.content: Russia said that its military forces were still fighting what President Vladimir Putin labeled an antiterrorist operation in the Belgorod region.

entry.title: Bills Restricting Care for Trans Teens Skyrocket
entry.content: Sixteen states have placed broad new restrictions on gender-affirming healthcare for transgender minors this year, with 16 others having introduced similar bills.
